#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/chat.rst:219
msgid "Generate Models"
msgstr "生成モデル"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/chat.rst:224
msgid ""
"The Generate API mirrors OpenAI's legacy `Completions API "
"<https://platform.openai.com/docs/api-reference/completions/create>`__."
msgstr ""
"Generate API は、OpenAI の `Completions API "
"<https://platform.openai.com/docs/api-reference/completions/create>`__ "
"を再現しています。"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/chat.rst:226
msgid ""
"The difference between the Generate API and the Chat API lies primarily in "
"the form of input. Opposite to the Chat API that takes a list of messages as"
" input, the Generate API accepts a freeform text string named \"prompt\"."
msgstr ""
"Generate API と Chat API の主な違いは入力形式にあります。Chat API "
"はメッセージのリストを入力として受け取り、Generate API は prompt という名前の自由テキスト文字列を入力として受け取ります。"

